여러분. 청소를 하다보니 제가 오늘 왜 불쾌함을 겪어야 했는지 깨닫게 되었습니다. 왜냐면 제가 ‘그냥 이렇게 살면서 서서히 잊혀질 수 있지 않을까, 그저 평범한 회사원으로 살 수 있지 않을까,’ 그런 생각을 요새 했기 때문입니다. 제 논문을 짜른 호로자식들이 생각나고 또 좀 아깝긴 해도, 제 지식이랄 것은 결국 당신들의 문제는 그리 대단한 게 아니다, 뭐 이런 것 뿐이고, 양자역학이 없다면 전구에 불이 들어오지 않을거라고 믿는 못배운 사람이 교수도 하고 한국을 대표하는 지식인을 계속 하더라도 전구에는 불이 들어올 것이기 때문입니다. 돈 또한. 제 몫이 얼마나 할까요? 받아내면 좋겠지만 책임이 따를 것이고, 그렇게 큰 돈을 가지고서는 한가하게 살 수는 없겠지요. 저의 상처들, 흉터들도 언젠가는 사라질 것이니까요. 그런 생각을 하다보니 이 머저리 같은 녀석들이 ‘이곳은 더러운 곳이다, 이곳은 살기 힘든 곳이다, 너가 그런 생각을 한다면 너를 불쾌하게 할 것이다,‘ 라는 메세지를 전하게 된 것이지요.

저는 31살 일용직 노가다 꾼입니다.
현재는 사고로 병원에 입원 해 있구요. 아버지는 따로 계시지 않고 어머니께서 혼자 저를 키우셨는데 4년전부터 몸이 많이 좋지 않아서 요양병원에 계십니다. 병원비는 제가 하루하루 벌어서 월 마다 모아 입금하고 있어 잘 계십니다. 
헌디 저번주에 제가.. 닥트 공사판에서 일을 하다 2층에서 구조물과 함께 추락 하는 바람에 저는 물론 밑에 사람 두명까지 같이 다치게 되었습니다. 하청업체 보험사에서 산재처리는 한다고 하나.. 일용직이라 힘들수도 있다는 답변을 듣게 되었습니다.
또한 저의 구조물로 인해 다치신 두분의 병원비는 보험 처리가 되지 않아 제가 병원비나 한분은 입원 한분은 경상이라 통원이라 제가 비용을 떠 맡게 되었습니다.
이런 커뮤니티에 글을 쓰는게 솔직히 말해서 될까 싶습니다..
요즘 정말 사람들이 힘드신분들을 위해 기부를 많이 하시는데 
또함 사기도 많아 제 사연도 그럼 취급을 받게 될 것 같아서요..
뭐 하나 제대로 배운거 없이 고등학교 중퇴하고 검정고시 졸업하여 야간학교 기계 자동차 학과 다니면서 돈벌었으며, 학교와 공장직을 함께 하기엔 버겁다고 느껴져서 중퇴를 한 후에 바로 공사판 노가다로 뛰어 들었습니다. 돈은 꽤 모았습니다. 힘들었던 만큼.. 그리고 그 돈으로 부산 대연동 동네에 작게나마 자담치킨 체인점도 열었습니다. 허나 코로나 여파로.. 순식간에 무너 졌습니다. 남은 건 권리금에 대출 빛 이며... 배달도 많이 없고 빛만 늘어나 그만두고 다시 노가다 판에 뛰어 들었습니다.
하여 지금은.. 위에 말씀드린대로 사고가 나면서 너무 힘단 상황에 놓이게 되었습니다. 어머니껜 말씀드리지 못했고, 사회생활.. 네 할틈이 많이 없었어요 직장도 다녀보지도 못했고 내성적인 탓에 친구도 사귀지 못했습니다. 바보 같고 공사판만 다니는 제가 어디가서 도움을 요청할 곳도 없어서.. 마지막 지푸라기라도 잡는 심정으로 여기 글을 적었습니다... 간식비조차 없어.. 병원이 7인실인데 눈치가 많이 보입니다.. 다들 가족이 이것저것 넣어주고 구매도 하며 나눠먹고 하는데 눈치가 너무 보이고 제 자신이
자존감이 너무 떨어집니다.. 이대로 그냥 다 끝내고 싶구요..
도움을 요청하는 쓰레기같은 글 맞습니다.. 근데 정말 힘이 드네요...

동사무소에 전화해서 긴급 생계 지원을 받아보려 했고 129에 전화도 해봤습니다. 57만원정도가 3일안에 될 거 라고 말은 했지만 서류가 많이 필요하고, 제가 지금 서류를 떼러갈 수가 없는 몸입니다 다리가 안좋습니다.
그리고.. 경찰에도 도움을 요청해봤습니다 이리저리 전화를 많이 돌려쥬시고 도와주려 하셨지만, 잘 모르시는 것 같더라구요 지원이나 복지에 대해서.. 동사무소에선 좀 더 기다려야 할거라고 짧으면 2 주 한달도 걸릴 수도 있다고 합니다.

손태진님 덕분에 귀호강, 눈호강요

"가수 겸 아티스트[歌手 兼 アーティスト]"인 
"심수봉[沈守峰, 본명(本名) : 심민경(沈玟卿)]"씨의 
"백만송이 장미[百万本のバラ]"랑 "가수(歌手)"인 
"이수영[李秀英, 본명(本名) : 이지연(李知姸)]"씨의 
"그리고 사랑해[そして愛してる]"랑 비슷한

Do you have questions about Jesus Christ or how to get to Heaven 😇? With a moment of your time, we can discuss the topic!


1. So Heaven 🌤 let's start there, how do you go there? Well you can be invited into Heaven the same way you invite people into your house 🏡 So who do you invited into your house: friends, family, dates, good neighbors etc... What do all of them have in common?

2. They all have a good relationship with you 🫂 You enjoy each others company, you talk and want to learn more about one another! 

3. People you have good relationship with are more likely to enter your house than: 😈  Enemies, Fake-Friends, Strangers. These unwanted guest (trespassers ) just want to enter your house, not because they want you.

4. Everyone is welcome to Heaven except sin, and we need a relationship with Jesus✝️ because he cleanses our sins.
 
So out of all of this please keep these in mind.

•If you want to ascend to Heaven then you must follow the one descended from Heaven 🌤 

•If you want to live forever then you must go to the one who conquered death ☠ 

•If you want your sins to be forgiven then you want to go to the one who never sinned and always forgives.

So what's your relationship with Jesus like?

Thank you for your moment of your time!
God bless you! ♥

Jesus is coming back soon! The Bible foretold all of the things that are happening in the world right now over 2,000 years ago. The New World Order is about to come into power and the world is about to go into the 7 year tribulation, which is going to be literal hell on earth. Everything is coming together exactly like God said it would! Yes, for the world it is a hopeless situation, but the good news is that God has provided an escape through faith in Jesus Christ alone! 
     John 3:16: “For God so loved the world that he gave His one and only Son, that whoever believes in Him will not perish, but have everlasting life.”
      We are all born sinners and doomed to spend eternity in hell. Romans 3:10 states that “There is no one righteous, not even one”. 
     Romans 3:23 explains: “For all have sinned and fall short of the glory of God.” We all have a sin debt that we owe God and it is so great that we can never possibly repay it. However, the good news is that Jesus paid that debt by dying and suffering the wrath of God in our place on the cross, and three days later He rose from the dead in ultimate victory over sin and death. 
     Romans 6:23 says: “The wages of sin is death, but the gift of God is eternal life in Christ Jesus our Lord.” God loves us more than we can even imagine and is offering every single person forgiveness and salvation, regardless of what anyone has done, if only they repent and put their faith in Jesus Christ alone. We can never do anything to earn salvation no matter how good of a person that we think we are. Isaiah 64:6 states: “all our righteous acts are like filthy rags”. But praise God that when we accept Christ as our savior, Jesus gives us His righteousness! It’s a GIFT! 
     Romans 10:9-10 explains: “That if you confess with your mouth, “Jesus is Lord,” and believe in your heart that God raised him from the dead, you will be saved. For it is with your heart that you believe and are justified, and it is with your mouth that you confess and are saved.” 
     Romans 10:13 “Everyone who calls on the name of the Lord will be saved”. 

     Jesus IS Lord and the Bible says one day all will confess that and bow their knee before Him. Unfortunately, there will be many that do that right before they go into eternal torment in the lake of fire. Do it now before it is too late! Jesus is real, He is the Son of God, He gave His life for us, and three days later He rose from the dead. To this day there is an empty tomb in Jerusalem! He is coming back soon to rapture every true believer. Don’t be left behind to experience the wrath of God that’s about to fall on this world. Repent of your sins and get saved now before it’s too late. John 14:6: (Jesus speaking) “I am the way and the truth and the life. No one comes to the Father except through me.”

В конце 1902 года президент США Теодор Рузвельт отправился в Миссисипи улаживать пограничный спор между этим штатом и соседней Луизианой. В свободный от переговоров день гостя пригласили на охоту. Добыть зверя не удалось, и, чтобы ублажить президента, ему поставили под выстрел заранее пойманного медвежонка. Но Рузвельт стрелять отказался. Газета «Вашингтон пост» поместила рассказ об этом происшествии.

Через несколько дней владелец бруклинской лавки канцелярских товаров Моррис Мичтом выставил у себя в витрине тряпичного медведя, снабдив его табличкой: Teddy’s Bear (медведь Тедди, то есть Теодора). Желающих купить игрушку оказалось так много, что Мичтом даже основал компанию по ее производству.

За плюшевым мишкой закрепилось имя Тедди. А Теодор Рузвельт, в 1904 году повторно баллотируясь в президенты, сделал медведя своим талисманом и победил.

Imagine if you died right now, where would your soul go for eternity? Was everything you ever did without purpose, and never really mattered, or will you just stop existing, after you draw your last breath? Think about this, it is the most important question of your life. There is only one chance to get it right, and it is in this lifetime. Do not be deceived, God is not mocked; for whatever a man sows, that he wil also reap. Heaven is real, place of eternal bliss, peace, and perfection. Hell is real, place of eternal suffering, torment and agony. You're going to spend your eternity in one of those places. God's will is, that nobody would perish. One day, each and everyone of us must appear before the Judgement Seat of The Holy Righteous God, and to give an account, how we have lived our life. The only way to get to Heaven is, if you've never broken any part of The God's Law, in other words, if you're without sin, and every single one of us have sinned. Not one person, who's not born again from above, of The Holy Spirit of God, and is still in their sins, can inherit The Kingdom of God, for the wages of sin is death, and eternal damnation. Our sins separates us from God. 

 But The Heavenly Father in His love and mercy, sent His only begotten Son, Jesus Christ, to atone for our sins. He left Heaven's Throne, was God in flesh, conceived by The Holy Spirit, born of a virgin, lived a holy perfect life while being in same temptations as we are, yet without sin, was condemned unjustly to death, although being innocent, was beaten, mocked, flogged, and crucified on the cross and gave up His life and Blood willingly on our behalf, for there is no forgiveness of sins without the shedding blood, but Christ, The spotless and unblemished Lamb of God, The Final Perfect Sacrifice once and for all, took the punishment of our sins on the cross, sacrificed Himself for us and paid the sin debt in full, and future, so we can be forgiven of all our sins, and be redeemed back to God, after the fall in Paradise by satan's tempting, through The Holy Precious Blood, which Jesus shed on the middle cross of Calvary, in His everlasting love towards every single one of us. 

 If you truly repent, confess your sins, and ask for forgiveness of all your sins from The Lord Jesus Christ, The Holy One of Israel, and believe with all your heart, that Jesus Christ of Nazareth, The Messiah, The Son of The One and only True Living God, was crucified at Calvary, died on the cross for our sins, was burried, rose from the dead by God's power on the third day according to The Holy Bible, and by faith receive Him as your Lord and Savior, through The Holy Royal Blood of Jesus Christ you will be saved, and are born again from above, of The Holy Spirit of God. Every sin that weighs down your inner being, even the ones you never dare to speak of, will be forgiven. Repent, believe, follow Christ, and you will spend your eternity in Heaven with our Holy Almighty God, where is no more death, sorrow, pain nor crying.  

 John 3:16 - For God so loved the world, that He gave His only begotten Son (Jesus Christ), that whosoever believeth in Him, shall not perish, but have everlasting life.

 John 14:6 - Jesus saith unto him: "I am The Way, The Truth, and The Life. No man cometh unto The Father (to Heaven), except through Me.". 

 John 6:47 - (Jesus said unto them:) "Verily, verily, I say unto you: He that believeth on Me, hath everlasting life." 

 The Book of Acts 4:12 - Neither is there salvation in any other: for there is none other name under Heaven given among men (only Jesus Christ), whereby we must be saved. 

 Romans 10:9-10 - That if thou shalt confess with thy mouth The Lord Jesus, and shalt believe in thine heart, that God hath raised Him from the dead, thou shalt be saved. For with the heart man believeth unto righteousness; and with the mouth confessions is made unto salvation. 

 Romans 10:13 - For whosoever shall call upon the name of The LORD (Jesus Christ), shall be saved.

 Romans 8:1-2 - There is therefore now no condemnation to them, which are in Christ Jesus, (born again from above, of The Holy Spirit.) For the law of The Spirit of life in Christ Jesus, hath made me free from the law of sin and death. 

 Ephesians 2:8-10 - For by grace are ye saved, through faith; and that not of yourselves; it is the gift of God; not of works, lest any man should boast. For we are His workmanship, created in Christ Jesus, unto good works, which God hath before ordained, that we should walk in them. (According to The Holy Bible, salvation is completely, entirely, and 100% by faith in Jesus Christ, by His mercy, and work of the cross. God sees us worthy in Christ. We can't earn it by our good deeds, and we're not kept saved by our good deeds, God's will is, that we'd do them, but He has given us free will.) 

Titus 3:5 - Not by works of righteousness, which we have done, but according to His mercy, He (Christ) saved us, by the washing of regeneration, and renewing of The Holy Spirit. 

 Isaiah 1:18 - "Come now, and let us reason together, saith The LORD. Though your sins be as scarlet, they shall be as white as snow. Though they be red like crimson, they shall be as wool."  

1 Timothy 2:5 - For there is one God, (God of Abraham, Isaac, and Jacob), (Jacob = Israel), and one Mediator between God and men, The Man Christ Jesus. (There is only one God, in three different Persons: The Father, The Son and The Holy Spirit. This is called; The Holy Trinity. There are not three different Gods, but only one God, in three different Persons.) 

 The Book of Revelation 1:8 - (Jesus Christ said:) "I am The Alpha and The Omega, The Beginning and The Ending, says The Lord God; who is, who was, and who is to come, The Almighty." (The King of Kings and Lord of Lords.) 

 1 Peter 5:8 - Be sober, be vigilant; because your adversary the devil, as a roaring lion, walketh about, seeking, whom he may devour.  

John 10:10 - (Jesus said unto them:) "The thief (satan) cometh not, but for to steal, and to kill and to destroy: I am come, that they might have life, and that they might have it more abundantly." 

 The Book of Revelation 22:12 - (The Lord Jesus Christ said:) "And, behold, I come quickly; and My reward is with Me, to give every man according, as his work shall be."

If courage is not enough, then continue as if nothing happened and by doing this you will show that despite the mistake you can continue and not ruin the concert, you know how to behave on stage. But there is a big difference. I am mature and accustomed to life. They are just kids who don't know what to do on the way to their dreams. Рора, забывшая слова песни на ежемесячном прослушивании такая милая 🥰 И мне хочется отдать должное Ян Хён Соку за его поддержку этих молодых талантов ❤Он бывает строгим, но он в то же время может подтолкнуть трейни к их самосовершенствованию. Даже спустя столько лет он находит талантливых людей, которые раскрываются впоследствии и становятся настоящими бриллиантами. У Ян Хён Сока действительно талант находить таланты 😊И что, я замечаю уже в который раз это взаимоотношения между участницами. Уже в 3х видео я вижу поддержку участниц друг друга. Все они ещё очень юные, поэтому поддержка очень важна. Когда в группе царит покой, взаимопонимание, уважение, страсть к музыке и танцам а также всё это завершает настоящий талант, то эту группу должен ждать успех. Что меня удивило, так это то, что Рора в таком юном возрасте такая рассудительная. И слова Ян Хён Сока : Я выбрал для неё имя Рора, потому, что верю, что она станет настоящим артистом. И будет сиять, как Аврора 💖 У Роры по настоящему потрясающий голос. P.S Рора и Чикита одни из самых милых макнэ лайн, что я видела. Милее пока, что мои любимые Розэ и Лиса 😅

- 예슈아커밍 / Yeshua Coming -

천국은 우주 밖에 있습니다. 거리상 너무나도 멀고도 먼 거리에 있습니다. 이 시간도 사람들의 영혼은 빛과 같이 올라갔다 내려 갔다 하고 있습니다. 올라가는 빛은 사람들의 영혼이 인생을 졸업하고 천국 고향으로 가는 것이고, 내려오는 빛은 하나님의 신묘막측한 목적과 함께 이 땅에 내려 오는 새 사람들의 탄생을 의미합니다. 지금 이 순간도 전세계 각 언어로 사람들의 기도와 찬양과 예배들은 마치 데이타베이스화 되어서 빛으로 도로로록 천국으로 올라가고 있으며, 하나님은 실시간 사람들의 모든 기도를 다 듣고 계십니다. 하나님은 시간과 공간을 초월하시고, 어제, 오늘, 내일 영원히 존재하는 분이시며, 이 시간도 주무시지도 졸지도 않고, 순수 천상의 언어 방언의 언어로 전세계, 전하늘, 전 우주에 둥둥둥 떠 다니시며 일하고 계십니다. 창조주 그분의 이름은 야훼, 성령님, 예슈아이십니다. 예슈아를 믿지 않는 사람들은 그 영혼이 땅에서 떨어지지도 않습니다. 예슈아를 믿는 것이 얼마나 중요한 것인지 이 땅을 살아 가면서 꼭 아셔야 합니다. 예슈아는 진짜 하나님이시며, 아주 곧 거룩한 선택 받은 하나님의 백성들을 위해서 거룩한 천국소속 천군천사들과 함께 아주 어마무시한 영광으로 오신다고 합니다. 거룩한 하나님의 백성으로써 영적으로 준비하셔야 합니다. 휴거의 순간이 오면, 강력한 창조주 하나님의 영적인 광채가 선택 받은 자들의 영혼과 육체와 정신과 마음과 세포 하나 하나, DNA 하나 하나까지 다 스며들며, 눈 깜짝할 사이에 아주 빛으로 가득하고, 썩어질 육체가 영원히 썩지 않을 영적인 존재로 빛으로 변해서 싹 위로 올라 갑니다. 휴거를 스스로 거룩함으로 준비하세요.  모든 영광과 찬양, 경배 오직 야훼, 성령님, 예슈아께 올려드립니다. 오직 예슈아!

Heaven is outside the universe. In terms of distance, it is far, far away. Even at this time, people's souls go up and down like light. The ascending light means that people's souls graduate from life and go to their hometown in heaven, and the descending light signifies the birth of new people who come down to this earth with God's mysterious and mysterious purpose. Even at this moment, people's prayers, praises, and worship services in all languages ​​around the world are being made into a database and are going up to heaven with light again, and God is listening to all of people's prayers in real time. God transcends time and space, and exists forever yesterday, today, and tomorrow.
